The Telegraph - Calcutta : Nation

 BJP notice

 New 

 Delhi, Dec. 15: The BJP has given a notice under 

 Rule 184 of the Rules of Procedure and Business for a debate 

 on the Indo-US nuclear deal, which is scheduled for December 

 18 in the Lok Sabha. The rule entails voting. 

 The Centre has decided to oppose the move. Parliamentary affairs minister Priya Ranjan Das Munshi said the government would urge the Speaker to allow a short-duration discussion. 




